# This file defines the compiler options. It is read by dcc.

# This is used for debug builds.
#
# To do a debug build the environment variable CXXFLAGSFILE
# is set, to "CXXFLAGS.debug", which has dcc read this file
# instead of the default "CXXFLAGS".
#

-std=c++14 -Wall -Wextra -g
-g -O0
-UNDEBUG

